title: (Mon Full) We Recap Our Weekend At The iHeartRadio Music Festival + The Best and Worst Interactions We Had + Bobby's Superstition Is Back
itunes:title: (Mon Full) We Recap Our Weekend At The iHeartRadio Music Festival + The Best and Worst Interactions We Had + Bobby's Superstition Is Back
description:
We recap our weekend in Las Vegas for the iHeartRadio Music Festival, Lunchbox asked Bobby to introduce him to The Miz, and we hear the moment it happened. Plus, we share who we had the best and worst interaction with. Bobby's superstition is back after he forgot the princess necklace and Arkansas lost this weekend.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
